data.description: Oh so lovely and tucked away perfectly with just the right amount of privacy. Surrounded by magnificent evergreens, this wonderful 1 story home is in immaculate shape with a new roof, large trex deck, and many more updates. Living made easy...Enter to an open great room with a kitchen delivering great cabinets, tons of cooking and counter space, & a dining area ready to accommodate. Living room boasts tall windows gazing into the tree canopy, and lovely wood stove. Cozy but lives large with great space by design, pretty finishes, LVP & tile floors, stainless steel appliances. Beautiful tiling work in the bath sends this one over the top! Beautifully done yard fit for all your outdoor fun! Light, warm, & tastefully done at a great value.
